        <item>
            <title>3.11.2</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    No functional change to release 3.11.1.

                    <p>

                    <b>Bug fixes:</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Fixed update problem by switching from disk image files to zip files for distribution. Workaround for a problem which occurs when Sparkle tries to mount disk image file when updating Erbele (using disk image files seems to be incompatible with App Sandbox feature).</li>
                    </ul>
                ]]>
            </description>
