        <item>
            <title>3.11</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    This release improves packaging and distribution of the app.

                    <p>

                    <b>New:</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>native support for Apple Silicon architecture (distribution of Universal app)</li>
                        <li>introduced code signing and notarization of app, to fix Gatekeeper issues</li>
                        <li>enabled hardened runtime and App Sandbox, to improve security</li>
                    </ul>

                    <b>Improved:</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Updated Sparkle framework (used for app updates)</li>
                        <li>reduced file size of distributed disk image</li>
                    </ul>

                    <b>Other changes:</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>documented support for macOS Monterey</li>
                    </ul>
                ]]>
            </description>
            <pubDate>Thu, 04 Nov 2021 22:04:22 +0100</pubDate>
